                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t18000115-73-off433" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000115-73-off433" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000115-73-off433" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18000115-73-cd434" type="crimeDate">27th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000115-73-off433 t18000115-73-cd434"></join>, three coats, value 40s. a pair of breeches, value 10s. three waistcoats, value 18s. a pair of shoes, value 2s. and fourteen pounds in monies numbered, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18000115-73-victim637" type="victimName">
                           Joseph 
                           Purcox
                        <interp inst="t18000115-73-victim637" type="surname" value="Purcox"></interp>
